name: Grilled Chicken Thighs (feat. Eze Jackson)
description:
The instrumental evolved and the pandemic wave settled. I had a few folks over to spit on the mic, and after sanitizing, I added a few vocals myself. Eze wrote the hook. #epicfam and #baltimore in the building.
